comment: Backed this on Kickstarter. The unique and beautiful key art and varied gameplay across sessions is what drew me to this game (family likes to play the same game over and over). Suffers from analysis paralysis at times, but for me that's part of the fun of games that enable and encourage strategy. When I need to travel to a con, and want to take a along big box game experience but I can't spare the space in my bag, Unlocked is my #1 companion.
